Package: ciberAMP
Title: mRNA and copy number data integrative algorithm.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Rubén", "Fernández", email = "ruben.fdez.caloto@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: ciberAMP performs copy number and mRNA expression data integration. It allows users to finde out copy number-driven gene's differential expression. It uses GISTIC and RNAseq data from TCGA to analyze the more than 11.000 samples across 33 different tumor cohorts.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
biocViews: SCNAs, RNAseq, copy number alteration, copy number and expression integration
